<paragraph id="8BBCC323FFA8FF82FF67FAA48699FAF4" blockId="22.[168,775,1162,1872]" pageId="22" pageNumber="1025">
Phanerophytes; endemic to mountain ranges of 
<collectingRegion id="49C70DC1FFA8FF82FF01FAFA86F6FADA" box="[168,424,1343,1367]" country="Argentina" name="Buenos Aires" pageId="22" pageNumber="1025">Buenos Aires province</collectingRegion>
. Critically Endangered, reasons unknown (
<bibRefCitation id="EF92BED2FFA8FF82FEB0FADB86E2FAF4" author="Delucchi G" box="[281,444,1377,1401]" pageId="22" pageNumber="1025" pagination="19 - 31" refId="ref30263" refString="Delucchi G (2006) Las especies vegetales amenazadas de la Provincia de Buenos Aires: una actualizacion. Aprona Boletin Cientifico 39: 19 - 31." type="journal article" year="2006">Delucchi 2006</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
